info.name: Interrogation
info.attribution:
Suspect by Adrien Coquet from NounProject.com

The wood background by Nathan Dumlao is from-https://unsplash.com/photos/J2gEgTPM_OA and is available under the Unsplash license.

The images of the people, are all generated by https://thispersondoesnotexist.com.

The name list is from https://www.ssa.gov/OACT/babynames/.

The room design, library image, and other room elements are by Ingegneus and are released to the public domain under CC0.
info.description: Take turns asking characteristics questions about photos to deduce the secret person your opponent has been assigned. First person to guess correctly wins.
info.similarDesigner: Theo Coster, Ora Coster, Theora Design
